dmca.title: Copyright infringement claim by Here Network (dinehere.ca)
dmca.body:
-----Original Message-----
From: Chad DeGroot [mailto:chad@dinehere.ca] 
Sent: Tuesday, January 23, 2007 2:43 PM
To: Copyright
Cc: 'Roger Williams'; Mike@dinehere.ca
Subject: Copyright infringement claim by Here Network (dinehere.ca)

Hello,

We have recently submitted a copyright infringement claim by facsimile.
I wanted to make sure that this was received properly. It has been
attached for your convenience to make copying URLs easier for inspection
of the claim. Please let me know if the fax was not received or if you
have any questions or comments.

Regards,
~Chad
